{"tid":174451,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[求教]好唔好去新加坡exchange？","createTime":"2017-03-26T19:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T11:59:46.000Z","uid":163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"489b3446414247b31505b6f8808594971c1fc045","tid":174451,"uid":163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T19:55:43.000Z","msg":"話說小弟收到新加坡嘅exchange offer 係去NTU（南洋理工）<br />\n依家猶疑緊take唔take呢嗰offer<br />\n因為我本身係aim去英國 話曬去浸下鹹水 練下英文 體驗西方文化 重點係方便歐遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人覺得新加坡同香港無乜分別<br />\n同埋好似好悶咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剛剛又做左少少research 發覺嗰邊讀書都幾chur下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗唯一好處係真係可以識到世界各地的人 D人成日吹奏新加坡D大學係小型聯合國<br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人嘅巴/絲打俾D意見？thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4770b6c2f1048d7ee9b6bc559c5ab130eaac6576","tid":174451,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T19:57:24.000Z","msg":"有邊到讀書唔chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa157944baf0ee1d57b3dfe1190873065bb0c289","tid":174451,"uid":24177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T20:00:21.000Z","msg":"果邊讀書會辛苦過香港"},{"pid":"6194b12f27831c950591b6cd2e7a559cd7383cd3","tid":174451,"uid":163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:16:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3d07447243e33dcaec84d20b9f751a05c140605","tid":174451,"uid":72967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:16:34.000Z","msg":"個到又悶又chur<br />\n緊係去英國啦"},{"pid":"8de5ce9f3403719a5761542640189b13e06b22fc","tid":174451,"uid":77697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:30:03.000Z","msg":"有得去uk緊係去uk啦<br />\nsg係比你當後路"},{"pid":"a2c40e44f6a09b326ec5910521a3d8d2aceee71a","tid":174451,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edeba9c7ef3dc30389296af9ba9e5be26b3a8c56","tid":174451,"uid":99172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:05:48.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇其他offer?<br />\n冇但又想去exchange咪去囉"},{"pid":"d407380f971c899f1002dcbb22dfa01910908888","tid":174451,"uid":78914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:15:35.000Z","msg":"你去exchange都係要pass jeh 應該唔難<br />\n不過嗰邊local students讀書真係chur過香港<br />\n<br />\n利申 去過sg exchange"},{"pid":"87ca663ecf611db8090844fb48b552d7b49fe7e5","tid":174451,"uid":19703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"exchange去到都係求pass咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0330dfc086a1f307c819cdc8adee38127f92a70e","tid":174451,"uid":163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你去exchange都係要pass jeh 應該唔難<br />\n不過嗰邊local students讀書真係chur過香港<br />\n<br />\n利申 去過sg exchange</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗯明白<br />\n咁你去嗰時覺得點？有冇新體驗？"},{"pid":"d96f4c27fd11db93ac7ba6cad9d86d99ac41f543","tid":174451,"uid":78914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你去exchange都係要pass jeh 應該唔難<br />\n不過嗰邊local students讀書真係chur過香港<br />\n<br />\n利申 去過sg exchange</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗯明白<br />\n咁你去嗰時覺得點？有冇新體驗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我其實幾鍾意新加坡 雖然同香港係似 但始終都有佢地唔同嘅地方 文化已經好唔同<br />\n同埋真係可以識到來自唔同地方同文化嘅人 <br />\n仲有嗰邊啲professor都高質過香港好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2deb07d16a6f758451e21500c507be53b1e309","tid":174451,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim